{"tid":1076660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【得公屋得天下！】排8年獲330呎40年樓齡公屋   私樓豪裝間3間房 (含工人房)！","createTime":"2019-03-25T04:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T10:29:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"e4a5d427572703e034bbd8d9ae3300199955dfbc","tid":1076660,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:23:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_OEXNdGo_2c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_OEXNdGo_2c&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=7f7f46a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_OEXNdGo_2c</a><br />\n<br />\n輪候公屋，是一場持久戰，不少人等到心灰意冷&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n「其實真的等了很長時間，作為香港人，都等了8年以上的時間，再要等的話，其實會感到極度失望。」Eric（化名）一家四口，半年前獲派九龍區一個330呎公屋單位，但已經是40年樓齡的舊屋邨，「只要地區合理，就算比較殘舊，都可以接受。」他覺得，自己已比很多人幸運。<br />\n<br />\n他坦言，已輪候了一段長時間，「由最初二人輪候，到後來兩個兒子出世，由二人變四人，現在幼子已經七歲多，排了足足八年有多。」<br />\n<br />\n未獲派公屋前，一家人租樓住，「租住私人單位，不過是分層住宅，即是各自有出入門口，跟劏房有些少分別，就是空間會比較大，大約有三百呎，當時租金都要萬多元。」他說負擔很重，因租金差不多佔整體家庭收入一半。<br />\n<br />\n他沒想過，申請公屋這麼難，「其實以前不是太覺得（困難），因為八年前開始輪候時，是說三年可以上樓，怎知好像《無間道》般，三年之後又三年，過了六年還未輪候到的時候，就會有點絕望。一來小朋友開始長大，居住環境實在太擠逼，但又負擔不了太昂貴的私人樓宇，所以作為一個市民，對政府政策都會覺得有點無奈。」<br />\n<br />\n能夠上樓，總算解決居住問題，他決定用盡積蓄將單位裝修得好一點、舒服點，令家人有一個比較舒適的環境。"},{"pid":"283125c0a2dc79eae848f567247ae620853420a2","tid":1076660,"uid":134006,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:24:40.000Z","msg":"三百呎左右仲要間多工人房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a769210794484db8533044cf6f111d4357861b9","tid":1076660,"uid":134006,"like":24,"dislike":7,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"設計得好撚7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853f67ecf421d08f9f8a3dfa5ce5812a2bcb07e6","tid":1076660,"uid":79563,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"quote":{"pid":"283125c0a2dc79eae848f567247ae620853420a2","tid":1076660,"uid":134006,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:24:40.000Z","msg":"三百呎左右仲要間多工人房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:26:13.000Z","msg":"香港人就快訓街都要工人"},{"pid":"2d733f98563b733a31924f095d21f129d07fac14","tid":1076660,"uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"0a769210794484db8533044cf6f111d4357861b9","tid":1076660,"uid":134006,"like":24,"dislike":7,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"設計得好撚7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:26:38.000Z","msg":"主人房之外, 其他都OK喎<br />\n<br />\n我細個住公屋, 都無咁正"},{"pid":"dae0ce3a86829a8817f60a000e3243bf33a2c044","tid":1076660,"uid":66436,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:30:47.000Z","msg":"好撚葡萄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申租緊樓"},{"pid":"0631aead86a7ba742bc1fe2c39fb2e61b001e88c","tid":1076660,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dae0ce3a86829a8817f60a000e3243bf33a2c044","tid":1076660,"uid":66436,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:30:47.000Z","msg":"好撚葡萄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申租緊樓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:34:07.000Z","msg":"得公屋得天下！"},{"pid":"10d32b55c503b8b441bcf87e065663f4a59434d4","tid":1076660,"uid":38607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:54:47.000Z","msg":"食飯位喺邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f764dc923495c28ca4eb48716b4b7